<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dormitory Land Tender Price Calculator</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://gc.kis.v2.scr.kaspersky-labs.com/FD126C42-EBFA-4E12-B309-BB3FDD723AC1/main.js?attr=EYCTcSRd_YSzi8oKXiPXCmIWv8RNpBz55Ph3XczXP4RklGBbWkiEACgu8-KW1EevvUQENmXTxTOACrkRswCUHbALB8xwpydDCuWlrDBgstPPR7WUHoI_ftYWE7YFy8VWeULs2jEtBUf8PqwGoeqXpXiP6xTXQs406-Ip2i3KRz0hpcgFui-XcX8KMmbSybpPwbszKkkAWHx2uFYKZr2cbXDLFoWY3bau02y7XTHunMbEbeZBjiM_sUheG2rW-je_RbbWN9aDBPtH9XdEPQmKkt55T1GXl9tauU0cK-V2cNjppavC1J903DMs9DIA3RAmcu2zFjF4Su73pgxUosguLvyZdRm-9rVuVHz8HGiDq4Ymv3mXouldio7BbnRr17K3bKmUN54_h9VtxUbIQcl9NTOu8ecFPi0Jgii9wnUoK2GavUzHaqw6GbUZ0hB3dJSWH5S6RBBxtdQDf_v0ab3jKG8DzV11bnIZGE_xyjdav4ED9nX0c4P--J8SxdL5yROfkDTaxuFONy-hTrd5THmBpAh7Obw9i4rNYkhjj9SzmmrI8639c0e_875t0zkuQt2pN9pWZVQzYvFgNbMJ6dlq45CaK4IaypE-ZJ0tZD4a-wMzS9RkBoumms3vW3mBN4QJfkxyBKg3v1NGJT4be6wM0g3XmOcz-pbodHdryERxAIYAJsd5HUhH2yM2B5Rq6GWE" charset="UTF-8"></script><link rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous" href="https://gc.kis.v2.scr.kaspersky-labs.com/E3E8934C-235A-4B0E-825A-35A08381A191/abn/main.css?"/><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a3a5c;
            --secondary: #2c5282;
            --accent: #38a169;
            --accent2: #d69e2e;
            --danger: #e53e3e;
            --light: #f7fafc;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --text: #2d3748;
            --text-light: #718096;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: var(--light);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        header {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        header p { opacity: 0.9; font-size: 0.95rem; }

        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        @media (max-width: 900px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .card h2 .icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .form-group input, .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            background: #fafafa;
        }
        .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--secondary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(44,82,130,0.1);
            background: white;
        }
        .form-group .hint {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .input-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .input-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .btn {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .btn:hover { background: var(--secondary); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
        .btn-block { width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin-top: 10px; }

        .results-section { display: none; }
        .results-section.active { display: block; }

        .price-cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) { .price-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .price-card {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .price-card.conservative { background: #fff5f5; border: 2px solid #feb2b2; }
        .price-card.medium { background: #f0fff4; border: 2px solid #9ae6b4; }
        .price-card.aggressive { background: #fffff0; border: 2px solid #fbd38d; }

        .price-card .label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .price-card.conservative .label { color: #c53030; }
        .price-card.medium .label { color: #276749; }
        .price-card.aggressive .label { color: #975a16; }

        .price-card .amount {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .price-card.conservative .amount { color: #c53030; }
        .price-card.medium .amount { color: #276749; }
        .price-card.aggressive .amount { color: #975a16; }

        .price-card .per-psf {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .price-card .reasoning {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-align: left;
            padding-top: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            color: var(--text);
        }
        .price-card .reasoning ul { margin: 8px 0 0 16px; }
        .price-card .reasoning li { margin-bottom: 4px; }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #ebf8ff;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .summary-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) { .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
        @media (max-width: 500px) { .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .summary-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .summary-item .value {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .summary-item .label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: #edf2f7;
            padding: 4px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .tab-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-light);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .tab-btn.active { background: white; color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        .tab-btn:hover:not(.active) { color: var(--text); }

        .tab-panel { display: none; }
        .tab-panel.active { display: block; }

        .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: right;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        th {
            background: #f7fafc;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
        }
        th:first-child, td:first-child { text-align: left; }
        tr:hover { background: #f7fafc; }
        .positive { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
        .negative { color: var(--danger); font-weight: 600; }

        .chart-container {
            position: relative;
            height: 350px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .info-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e6fffa;
            color: #234e52;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #b2f5ea;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin: 30px 0 15px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
        }

        .cashflow-legend {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .cashflow-legend span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
        .dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 3px; display: inline-block; }

        .tax-note {
            background: #fffaf0;
            border: 1px solid #fbd38d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #744210;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .final-profit {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
        .final-profit .label { font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .final-profit .amount { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .final-profit .sub { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 8px; }

        .toggle-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .toggle-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .toggle-label { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; }
        .toggle-desc { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); }

        .switch {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 44px;
            height: 24px;
        }
        .switch input { opacity: 0; width: 0; height: 0; }
        .slider {
            position: absolute;
            cursor: pointer;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: #cbd5e0;
            transition: .3s;
            border-radius: 24px;
        }
        .slider:before {
            position: absolute;
            content: "";
            height: 18px;
            width: 18px;
            left: 3px;
            bottom: 3px;
            background: white;
            transition: .3s;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        input:checked + .slider { background: var(--accent); }
        input:checked + .slider:before { transform: translateX(20px); }

        .scenario-selector {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .scenario-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .scenario-btn.active { border-color: var(--secondary); background: #ebf8ff; color: var(--secondary); }
        .scenario-btn:hover { border-color: var(--secondary); }

        .loading {
            display: none;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .loading.active { display: block; }
        .spinner {
            width: 40px; height: 40px;
            border: 4px solid var(--border);
            border-top-color: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
        }
        @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>🏗️ Dormitory Land Tender Price Calculator</h1>
        <p>Comprehensive financial modeling for Singapore dormitory developments with IRAS-compliant tax calculations, dual-loan structuring, and leasehold cashflow analysis.</p>
    </header>
    <div style="text-align: right; margin: 10px 0;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="generatePDF()" style="background: #2c5282; margin-right: 10px;">
            <span>📄</span> Export PDF Report
        </button>
        <button class="btn" onclick="window.print()" style="background: #4a5568;">
            <span>🖨️</span> Print
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- INPUT SECTION -->
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h2><span class="icon">📐</span> Land & Development Parameters</h2>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Land Size (sqm)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="landSize" value="10000" min="100">
                    <div class="hint">Gross site area in square metres</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Plot Ratio</label>
                    <input type="number" id="plotRatio" value="2.8" step="0.1" min="0.1">
                    <div class="hint">URA allowable plot ratio</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Leasehold Period (years)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="leasehold" value="60" min="1">
                    <div class="hint">Typically 30-60 years for dormitories</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Number of Pax (beds)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="numPax" value="1500" min="1">
                    <div class="hint">Total dormitory capacity</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Expected Occupancy (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="occupancy" value="85" min="0" max="100">
                    <div class="hint">Average annual occupancy rate</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Rental Rate per Pax/Month (S$)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="rentalRate" value="450" min="1">
                    <div class="hint">Monthly rental per bed space</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2><span class="icon">🏗️</span> Construction & Cost Parameters</h2>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Construction Cost per sqm (S$)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="constructionCost" value="2800" min="1">
                    <div class="hint">Typical dormitory: S$2,500–3,200/sqm</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Construction Period (months)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="constructionPeriod" value="24" min="1">
                    <div class="hint">From groundbreaking to TOP</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Professional Fees (% of construction)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="profFees" value="8" min="0" max="100">
                    <div class="hint">Architect, M&E, QS fees</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Contingency (% of construction)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="contingency" value="5" min="0" max="100">
                    <div class="hint">Buffer for cost overruns</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Other Development Costs (S$)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="otherDevCosts" value="500000" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">DC, legal, marketing, preliminaries</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Equity / Shareholder Capital (S$)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="equity" value="5000000" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Initial equity injection</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h2><span class="icon">🏦</span> Land Loan</h2>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>LTV Ratio (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="landLTV" value="60" min="0" max="100">
                    <div class="hint">Loan-to-value for land acquisition</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Interest Rate (% p.a.)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="landRate" value="4.5" step="0.1" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Current SIBOR + spread</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Repayment Period (months)</label>
                <input type="number" id="landTenor" value="240" min="1">
                <div class="hint">Total loan tenor in months</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2><span class="icon">🏗️</span> Construction Loan</h2>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>LTV Ratio (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="constructionLTV" value="70" min="0" max="100">
                    <div class="hint">Loan-to-cost for construction</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Interest Rate (% p.a.)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="constructionRate" value="5.0" step="0.1" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Typically higher than land loan</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Repayment Period (months)</label>
                <input type="number" id="constructionTenor" value="180" min="1">
                <div class="hint">Total loan tenor in months</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h2><span class="icon">⚙️</span> Operational Parameters</h2>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Monthly OpEx per Pax (S$)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="opexPerPax" value="85" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Utilities, cleaning, security, maintenance</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Fixed Monthly OpEx (S$)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="fixedOpex" value="15000" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Management, insurance, admin</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Annual Rent Escalation (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="rentEscalation" value="2.5" step="0.1" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Year-on-year rental growth</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Annual OpEx Escalation (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="opexEscalation" value="2.0" step="0.1" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Year-on-year cost growth</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2><span class="icon">💰</span> Financing & Returns</h2>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Shareholder Loan Interest (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="shLoanRate" value="6.0" step="0.1" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">If applicable, otherwise 0</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Shareholder Loan Amount (S$)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="shLoanAmount" value="0" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Subordinated shareholder financing</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Target IRR (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="targetIRR" value="12" step="0.5" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">Minimum acceptable project IRR</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Exit Cap Rate (%)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="exitCapRate" value="6.5" step="0.1" min="0">
                    <div class="hint">For terminal value estimation</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
        <h2><span class="icon">📊</span> Scenario Selection</h2>
        <div class="scenario-selector">
            <button class="scenario-btn active" data-scenario="medium" onclick="setScenario('medium')">Medium Case</button>
            <button class="scenario-btn" data-scenario="conservative" onclick="setScenario('conservative')">Conservative</button>
            <button class="scenario-btn" data-scenario="aggressive" onclick="setScenario('aggressive')">Aggressive</button>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-box" id="scenarioDesc">
            <strong>Medium Case:</strong> Base assumptions with moderate occupancy (85%), stable rental growth (2.5% p.a.), and standard construction costs. This represents the most probable outcome.
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-block" onclick="calculateAll()">
            <span>🚀</span> Calculate Tender Price & Cashflow Model
        </button>
    
        <button class="btn btn-block" onclick="window.print()" style="background: #4a5568; margin-top: 10px;">
            <span>🖨️</span> Print / Save as PDF
        </button></div>

    <!-- LOADING -->
    <div class="loading" id="loading">
        <div class="spinner"></div>
        <p>Crunching numbers and building your financial model...</p>
    </div>

    <!-- RESULTS SECTION -->
    <div class="results-section" id="results">

        <h2 class="section-title">🎯 Tender Price Recommendation</h2>
        <div class="price-cards">
            <div class="price-card conservative">
                <div class="label">Conservative</div>
                <div class="amount" id="conPrice">-</div>
                <div class="per-psf" id="conPsf">-</div>
                <div class="reasoning">
                    <strong>Why you SHOULD bid this:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Maximum downside protection</li>
                        <li>Higher probability of winning tender</li>
                        <li>Buffer against construction delays</li>
                        <li>Accommodates lower occupancy (75%)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <strong>Why you should NOT:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>May miss out if competition is fierce</li>
                        <li>Leaves money on the table</li>
                        <li>Lower absolute returns</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="price-card medium">
